The gentrification process
have sharply affected the indigenous

4
00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:15.650
and the black populations, for sure.

5
00:00:15.650 --> 00:00:20.340
The indigenous population
was the first to undergo this

6
00:00:20.340 --> 00:00:23.370
segregation and exclusion process,
thanks to the jesuits who arrived

7
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:25.620
at the coast.

8
00:00:25.620 --> 00:00:29.480
In their way from Piratininga
to Sao Paulo, they've killed

9
