11
00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:40.970
The colonization...

12
00:00:40.970 --> 00:00:46.880
The black population arrived
here in the 18th and 19th centuries.

13
00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:52.650
The biggest contingence were people
who came to work in coffee plantations.

14
00:00:52.650 --> 00:00:55.370
In that time, Sao Paulo
wasn't an influential city

15
00:00:55.370 --> 00:00:57.570
comparing to Rio, for example.

16
00:00:58.680 --> 00:01:01.450
It had 1/3 of Rio's population.

17
00:01:01.970 --> 00:01:06.910
After the so called abolition of
slavery, in 1888, the black population

18
00:01:07.420 --> 00:01:10.080
mostly made their living from trade.

19
00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:12.910
Given that trade was mostly done
by the black population,

20
00:01:12.910 --> 00:01:16.740
the streets were of high
importance to them,

21
00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:20.280
